==Min Nan==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ ko˥˧sɔ˨˩ ]}}

===Verb===
{{nan-verb|t|poj=kò-sò·|pojt=ko3soo3|tra=告訴|sim=告诉|rs=口04}}

# to file a lawsuit against

===Usage notes===
*Unlike Mandarin, kò-sò· does not mean ''to tell'' in Min Nan.  For that meaning, it is better to say: '''''kā''' + pronoun + '''kóng''''' (ex. ''Góa ū '''kā''' lín '''kóng'''-kòe'' - ''I '''told''' you'').